{"tid":1377750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以成功罷工？","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T15:56:04.000Z","uid":186938,"like":127,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff428be09f1d5ba6c5ef224d7b0b8362476355a","tid":1377750,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"第一次開post<br />\n<br />\n好多人唔敢罷工，都係因為驚同公司得自己罷，容易俾人mark住冇咗份工。<br />\n<br />\n其實如果知道夠人一齊罷工，就等於為所有有諗過罷工嘅人打返支強心針，實踐行動！<br />\n<br />\n所以我提議，準備罷工嘅人提早喺凌晨集合，例如中環，等大家知道罷工嘅at least 有幾多人，互相為大家增加勇氣！"},{"pid":"1f55377c6a37e72f54bccf4720792db08033a2fb","tid":1377750,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a174ae9f2ee6f6d484cecba4f47a8ae60f2740e1","tid":1377750,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1f81a768244ca1157c126b9ea530881f8e9d96","tid":1377750,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"好多人係唔同港鐵站入路/有野入路"},{"pid":"e1d4a8935acf3e9ca497dfbea25c5d61541a8e90","tid":1377750,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7593a2a574783488a9bdb97bffaeabc38339ccdf","tid":1377750,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:07.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 倡議民陣搞全港罷工「前夕」大遊行，一齊罷工吧！香港人！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1375198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1375198</a><br />\n<br />\n求下你地幫一幫推，<br />\n說好勇武之後和理非接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個運動要突破, 不要磨爛席<br />\n民陣提出全港大聯署,<br />\n參加者需出示自身行業，<br />\n要求民陣舉辦<br />\n遊行日子由8月3日至8月4日，<br />\n罷工日子: 自8月5日起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f9f2380f925c71c394ce835f2d55d9ad7fda79","tid":1377750,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b8d0ba5025c80dd8de7c15a9661e72b578f1b1e8","tid":1377750,"uid":44906,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"求下各位公務員同地鐵員工<br />\n只有你地罷工救到各位義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8f2a13e745c71cb7dbaf7ee0118b0d908450a4","tid":1377750,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"一齊罷！"},{"pid":"c9cbb5979a3cb3bfde561a08c269860f8544d229","tid":1377750,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd86c24d1cf0e82fa66b50a5b7cfff212addf779","tid":1377750,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"希望有高層帶頭罷工"},{"pid":"d14c763c7f8963330e496d2b463f94024af2de10","tid":1377750,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dd3c9d8ef8e6d795f64bb4b088da4e7043f14ee1","tid":1377750,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1216b79c445b217c2b5db11d9b977cdafa959a48","tid":1377750,"uid":186938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"39e031376913455e8cec6b81d58f5df916c331bf","tid":1377750,"uid":214192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"要傾定一個罷工日子<br />\n跟住做好文宣好似616咁"},{"pid":"a5aef632a141d83ab1b85f0c4091a21efc993e7b","tid":1377750,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"和理非手足，唔好俾勇武付出白費<br />\